    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "For non-C/C++ code we normalized as described in § II-C.\nFor C/C++ code, we also did experiments where we roughly\nidentiﬁed functions within C/C++ ﬁles using the following\nPerl regular expression:\n",
    "bbox": [
